{"tid":1032300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今鬧到個大陸婆差d喊","createTime":"2019-02-22T09:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T11:28:18.000Z","uid":40470,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d78fe1ff67ca14af3a0c2ea631fdcb89dd525d73","tid":1032300,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"今日行過上水天橋附近<br />\n<br />\n見到個三十幾歲大陸婆吐痰落地<br />\n<br />\n佢已經行前左幾步想走<br />\n<br />\n我迎面大大聲喝鳩佢問佢做乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n做乜撚野吐痰落地<br />\n<br />\n佢一開始口upup話神經病神經病想走<br />\n<br />\n直至我再大聲d屌柒佢話唔抹返個地唔好走<br />\n<br />\n佢就死死地氣拎紙巾出來抹個地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但死蝗蟲個賤格唔撚會改<br />\n<br />\n抹完地下張紙巾又係掉落地<br />\n<br />\n我靜左陣專登唔出聲等佢以為完事<br />\n<br />\n然後突然<br />\n<br />\n好撚大聲好撚大聲再喝鳩佢：<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母執返至好走！<br />\n<br />\n佢差d喊左出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n<br />\n今日傍邊睇到嘩嘩聲個幾隻中學雞勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab1a0c205a4fe90fe8c20172ce880f6da221824","tid":1032300,"uid":171451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"無圖無真相"},{"pid":"025c0b2479d5b0e003bf049ad3d2b92f94dc28bf","tid":1032300,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0ab1a0c205a4fe90fe8c20172ce880f6da221824","tid":1032300,"uid":171451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"無圖無真相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"即係要拍片影住佢抹地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好提意下次試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30a325bbc50bbde21686aded6d0d1e3a6007d01","tid"